import React from 'react' import { IoAirplaneSharp } from 'react-icons/io5' import { FlightData } from '../../models/FlightData' type FlightProps = { flight: FlightData } const getDayOfWeek = (dateString: string): string => { const date = new Date(dateString); const daysOfWeek = ["Sunday", "Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday"]; return daysOfWeek[date.getDay()]; }; const InfoFlight: React.FC = ({flight}) => { return (
{flight.departure?.icao}
{flight.departure?.timezone}
left {flight.departure?.gate}
{flight.departure?.airport} - {flight.flight?.icao}
{ flight.departure?.actual ? `${getDayOfWeek(flight.departure.actual.slice(0, 10) ?? '')} ${flight.departure.actual.slice(0, 10) ?? ''}` : `${getDayOfWeek(flight.departure?.estimated?.slice(0, 10) ?? '')} ${flight.departure?.estimated?.slice(0, 10) ?? ''}` }
{ flight.departure?.actual ? flight.departure.actual.slice(11) : flight.departure?.estimated?.slice(11) } { flight.flight_status === 'active' ? ' (on time)' : '' }
{flight.arrival?.icao}
{flight.arrival?.timezone}
arriving at { flight.arrival?.gate ? flight.arrival.gate : 'None' }
Charles de Gaulle/Roissy - CDG
TUESDAY 16-JUL-2024
(33 minutes early) 06:12AM CEST
6h 27m elapsed
3,280 mi flown
5h 55m remaining
3,204 mi to go
) } export default InfoFlight
